dfischer.utils

Class AlertGenericNotificationInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.AlertConfigGenericNotification
      • dfischer.utils.AlertGenericNotificationInstance

  • public class AlertGenericNotificationInstance
extends AlertConfigGenericNotification
    Real instance of an alert notification - objects of this class can be created and used at runtime. For example for sending notifications from a load test plug-in.
    Note: after creating an instance you can optionally call the method setMessageTextHTML(String messageTextHTML) in case if the alert device(s) support to send HTML messages.
    See Also:
    AlertConfigGenericNotification.setMessageTextHTML(String messageTextHTML), AlertConfigGenericDevice.sendNotification(AlertConfig alertConfig, AlertConfigGenericNotification genericNotification)

                                java.lang.String messagePrefix,

        Create an initialize a new instance.
        Parameters:
        notificationType - the notification type. Valid values are NOTIFICATION_TYPE_INTERNAL_ERROR, NOTIFICATION_TYPE_ERROR, NOTIFICATION_TYPE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED and NOTIFICATION_TYPE_INFO.
        messagePrefix - the additional message prefix
        messageHeadline - the headline of the message
